T1  - Waking Up from the American Dream: On the Experience of Young Americans during the Housing Boom of the 2000s
AU  - LAEVEN, LUC
AU  - POPOV, ALEXANDER
Y1  - 2017/08/01
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/jmcb.12408
